title: Match History not working
body: I know there has been a thread on this, but my comment went unanswered. My recent match history is failing to load, the borders and everything else loads just not the important stuff in the middle - it's just a clear slate. I really want to view some of it. I use a Mac OS X 10.9.5 (not sure if that helps in solving the issue).

replies.body:
Hi

Can you [send in a support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) on this?  I'd like to gather a bit of info from you so that we can troubleshoot it further.

Cheers
Mindstar
